345
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] na smislu.

346
00:36:23,199 --> 00:36:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] I taj crkveni brak se ne može raskinuti, može biti ništavan.

347
00:36:27,599 --> 00:36:31,360
